es/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n精闢"},{"pid":"5ac38fcc53685c3ae6a2e5eab2551e58e3086f61","tid":190652,"uid":36167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊科engine唔係男女比例嚴重失衡?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCity ee 男女比例6：4 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊有咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e328687869638a72244e25e58014f6315f0c86ac","tid":190652,"uid":11283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你老味<br />\nMech 真係 engine 入面最多野讀<br />\n<br />\n首先由 Mechanics 開始<br />\n由普通kinematics , Kinetics of particle 玩到 vibration, damping, 2/3 degree of freedom， dynamics and control  再撈埋ODE PDE玩， 之後再加埋robotics 諗起都興奮<br />\n普通static 就玩 bending , statically undetermined beam 深入啲再玩 finite element analysis <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後solid 加埋Material , 讀啲dislocation ，bonding  仲有 processing method, heat treatment 9千幾萬種野背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nMechanics + material 之後可以做埋design of machines . Gear drive, belt drive, chain drive <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外一邊有thermofluids<br />\n由最簡單嘅 thermodynamics 讀起，之後到 vapour compression cycle, refrigeration cycle, diesel cycle, Otto cycle，玩埋heat transfer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFluid 方面有 fluid mechanics, pipe flow, open channel flow, boundary layer, drag and lift 之後仲玩埋 flight mechanics <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係心血少啲都唔得<br />\n冇伏大家 各位DSE/ year 1 真係唔好簡mechan<br />\n施主回頭是岸啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n精闢</blockquote><br />\n屌，真係讀到死<br />\n利申 中緊伏"},{"pid":"b2e76a7adadbc39d9558db